### 📥 How to Use

Add to your `settings.gradle.kts`:
```kotlin
pluginManagement {
  resolutionStrategy {
    eachPlugin {
      if (requested.id.id.startsWith("dev.suresh.plugin")) {
        useVersion("${{TO_TAG}}")
      }
    }
  }
  repositories {
    gradlePluginPortal()
    mavenCentral()
  }
}

plugins { id("dev.suresh.plugin.repos") }
```

